013 |accessdate=8 May 2013 |archivedate=9 September 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130909185400/http://rfspro.ru/cgi-bin/player/script2.cgi?par1=119449 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nHe made his [[Russian Football Premier League]] debut on 7 March 2015 for [[FC Ural Sverdlovsk Oblast]] in a game against [[FC Zenit Saint Petersburg]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[Russian Football Premier League]]|url=http://rfpl.org/match/match_10470.html|title=Zenit-Ural game protocol|date=7 March 2015|accessdate=7 March 2015}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://news.sportbox.ru/Vidy_sporta/Futbol/stats/man_1315592486 Career summary by sportbox.ru] {{dead link|date=April 2020}} {{in lang|ru}}\n*{{Sportbox.ru|Futbol/Denis-Aleksandrovich-Fomin-Futbol-03051996}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fomin, Denis}}\n[[Category:1996 births]]\n[[Category:People from Kostanay Region]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Russia under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:FC Tekstilshchik Ivanovo players]]\n[[Category:FC Ural Yekaterinburg players]]\n[[Category:Russian Premier League players]]\n[[Category:FC Tambov players]]\n\n\n{{Russia-footy-defender-1996-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Russian football defender|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Eastern Slavic name|Aleksandrovich|Fomin}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| image = Denis Fomin.jpg\n| name = Denis Fomin\n| fullname = Denis Aleksandrovich Fomin\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1996|05|3|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = [[Lisakovsk]], [[Kazakhstan]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.85}}\n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| currentclub = [[FC Tekstilshchik Ivanovo]]\n| clubnumber = 17\n| years1 = 2013\u20132014 | clubs1 = [[FC Tekstilshchik Ivanovo]]          | caps1 = 54 | goals1 = 0 \n| years2 = 2015\u20132018 | clubs2 = [[FC Ural Sverdlovsk Oblast]]         | caps2 =  4 | goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2016      